drawTextWithEffect

public void drawTextWithEffect(Graphics2D g2,
                               String text,
                               double x,
                               double y,
                               double angle,
                               Font font,
                               Color forecolor,
                               Color blockout,
                               Color outlinecolor,
                               Color shadowcolor,
                               Color glowingcolor,
                               boolean corrector)
The method draws text with style, forecolor, blockout, outlinecolor, shadowcolor, glowingcolor.

Parameters:
g2 - Graphics2D to draw the string
text - textstring
x - the X coordinate where textstring center will be placed
y - the Y coordinate where textstring center will be placed
angle - angle from -90 to 90 degree, counter-clockwise
font - font to be drawn
forecolor - define the color of the textstring
blockout - define the color for blockout
outlinecolor - define the color for outline
shadowcolor - define the color of shadow
glowingcolor - define the color of glowing around the textstring
corrector - is optional parameter apply for special alignment for visual presentation of numeric text
